snippet.title: OK/NORMAL | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch out! It's time for another interactive PS1-esque experience by ME! 👉
https://store.steampowered.com/app/862580/OKNORMAL/
https://98demake.itch.io/oknormal

OK/NORMAL is a short, experimental third-person horror experience, inspired by early 3D console games of the 90's.  Journey through a dark, disjointed, dreamlike dimension with your cloud companion! Remember a good diet, take your medicine, and you should be fine!

98DEMAKE on Twitter and Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/98demake
https://twitter.com/98demake

If you would like to contact me for some reason, you can do that at: 98demake (at) gmail.com
